{"id": 3042, "genre": 1000, "title": "数字时代，你最想获得哪些小型“被遗忘权”？", "description": "其实我只想默默地上个网，并不是很希望得到那么多注意。（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA-Printstock）", "record_count": 9443, "comment_count": 12, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20191028193054yhRzBVCleFmYPt6E.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-10-28T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5996, "title": "数字时代，你最想获得哪些小型“被遗忘权”？", "content": "数字时代，你最想获得哪些“被遗忘权”？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 348979, "content": "历史信息删掉就是删掉，不用担心哪里还能找到", "image": "img/option/option/20191028175057bZ4tAqIihVlGJmzj.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348980, "content": "多年前发布的东西不会被人翻出来（甚至截图传播", "image": "img/option/option/201910281754544Im1adeGA7tbJBiM.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348981, "content": "匿名发布也是真的匿名，不需要担心被认出来", "image": "img/option/option/20191028175949ERLZNFhDISMuc26V.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348982, "content": "自己的账号不展示在社交平台搜索结果里", "image": "img/option/option/20191028180159FKUqTXYw8z9cNADQ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348983, "content": "自己的动态不展示在别人的 timeline 里", "image": "img/option/option/20191028181537OWl71fCMiD8ye4bJ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348984, "content": "社交媒体帐号随时可以注销 or 停用", "image": "img/option/option/20191028181813wDJ81WNYTcmlMsLv.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348985, "content": "一键隐身 or 不显示在线状态", "image": "img/option/option/20191028183119BjYpyLFDtAzcl54H.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348986, "content": "默默进群 or 退群，不用特意通知每个人", "image": "img/option/option/20191028184318k3U56lqYhi1rNKRg.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348990, "content": "给某个人的点赞，不用展示给所有好友/关注者", "image": "img/option/option/20191028205238h9ad3q8JmLzlTIcp.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 348987, "content": "这些不重要，我想要其他的权利", "image": "img/optio